      "height": 110,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "① Client sends grid update  →  compareAndSet() detects revision mismatch\n② BFF fetches authoritative revision  (Redis → MongoDB fallback)\n③ Sends private SyncRequired { currentRevision } → /user/queue/session\n④ Returns 409 ConcurrentModification\n⑤ Client receives SyncRequired → calls POST /sync\n⑥ POST /sync flushes Redis → MongoDB, returns SessionFullDto\n⑦ Client rehydrates grid, resumes editing",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 10,
      "containerId": null
